{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"97f9a1eade","title":"井冈山红卫兵第三号决议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3aad1f3d18","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":28,"articleId":"97f9a1eade"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"550a5d8a4b","name":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"14307ec972","type":"title","text":"井冈山红卫兵第三号决议","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"14e542bad0","type":"authors","text":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"2ec0a8145a","type":"paragraph","text":"成立原因","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"eeb0e7c190","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么要成立井冈山红卫兵？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"ae9044a84e","type":"paragraph","text":"在全国内，十六条的贯彻，遭到极大的阻力，革命造反精神没有得到充分发扬。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"8f94d20a92","type":"paragraph","text":"北京是如此，清华园内更是如此。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"587f66e1b4","type":"paragraph","text":"清华园内，清华大学红卫兵忠实地执行工作组的形“左”而实右的路线。毛泽东思想红卫兵则不敢抵制这条错误路线，使得这样一条错误路线畅通无阻。在八·二四以后充分暴露了他先天不足的软弱性。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"ac079e48e5","type":"paragraph","text":"为了坚决地抵制，反对这条形“左”实右的路线，坚决把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底，彻底完成毛主席交给我们的一斗二批三改的伟大任务。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"bfd69e2ece","type":"paragraph","text":"我们向清华大学全体革命师生员工郑重宣告：","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"9caaeff619","type":"paragraph","text":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵诞生了！他在无产阶级文化大革命的洪流中开航了。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"b9c9636020","type":"paragraph","text":"让我们高声欢呼，举起你的双手欢迎它吧！","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"7bba260836","type":"paragraph","text":"最后的胜利属于我们，未来的世界是属于我们的！","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"},{"id":"9ae2f94947","type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的领袖毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade"}],"page":{"id":"a10dbc8d43","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"97f9a1eade","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}